You could refactor this to add the event [supplier](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/function/Supplier.html) as an argument here:

```java
void sendEventToClients(Supplier<Event> eventSupplier) {
        Iterable<EntityRef> clients = entityManager.getEntitiesWith(ClientComponent.class);
        for (EntityRef client : clients) {
            client.send(eventSupplier.get());
        }
}
```

